Updated
=======
This map is an update of zm\_FireWaLL\_forestoutpost (http://gamebanana.com/csszm/maps/148209)

Introduction
============
Zombies are launching an assault on an outpost in the forest. Defend yourselves by blocking them with all sorts of obstacles, or find some high ground to fend yourselves from the zombies!

Features
========
- 64 + 64 spawnpoints
- Cubemaps
- Optimized
- Secrets

Changelog
=========
- The "hole" underneath the two-desk-room has been covered with a breakable wooden floor. Now you need to break it first. The cabinets underneath the desks are now physic props.
- The underground room design has been improved significantly.
- Shortcuts (ladders) up the tower have been added for balance reasons.
- Zombies should find it harder, if not impossible, to jump from the tower onto the tree-platform now.
- Map is now slightly brighter.
- Various textures have been replaced and improved
- New secrets have been added.
